OL,3,CMan jailed for 15 years for assaulting
OL,4,Ctwo people and killing grandfather
OL,6,FA man from Warwickshire who killed his
OL,7,Fgrandfather before he assaulted two
OL,8,Fvictims at a working men's club has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed for 15 years.
OL,11,FThe well known jaguar restoration
OL,12,Fexpert, 81-year-old John Brown, died
OL,13,Fsix days after being attacked in his
OL,14,Fhome by his grandson, Jakob Walpole,
OL,15,Fon November 23 last year.
