OL,3,CMan jailed for 15 years for assaulting
OL,4,Ctwo people and killing grandfather
OL,6,FThe jury at Warwick Crown Court found
OL,7,Fthe 33-year-old from Bulkington guilty
OL,8,Fof manslaughter, breaching a
OL,9,Frestraining order and two counts of
OL,10,Fassault, but cleared him of murder
OL,11,Fafter a three-week trial.
OL,13,FWalpole was handed the custodial
OL,14,Fsentence on today (Monday, August 4th)
OL,15,Fwith a further two years on extended
OL,16,Flicence.
OL,18,FThe court heard how the night that
OL,19,FWalpole attacked his grandfather, Mr
OL,20,FBrown 'stood up to' the defendant, who
OL,21,Fwas asking for money.
