OL,6,FMr Brown was then struck on the head
OL,7,Fby Walpole.
OL,9,FThe defendant sat in the dock at
OL,10,FWarwick Crown Court wearing a grey
OL,11,Ftracksuit with his head down while
OL,12,FJudge Kristina Montgomery KC sentenced
OL,13,Fhim and said: "(Mr Brown) was an
OL,14,Fexceptionally small man in
OL,15,Fdeteriorating physical health who had
OL,16,Fbeen diagnosed with dementia.
OL,18,F'You were an intimidating and
OL,19,Fpersistent nuisance in their lives'
