OL,4,Ctwo people and killing grandfather
OL,6,F"Your visits (to Mr Brown's home) were
OL,7,Fmade to exploit his love... by taking
OL,8,Fmoney from both your grandparents to
OL,9,Ffund your lifestyle. You were an
OL,10,Fintimidating and persistent nuisance
OL,11,Fin their lives."
OL,13,FWalpole repeatedly said "shut up" from
OL,14,Fthe dock while his mother Lynda Brown
OL,15,Fread a victim impact statement to the
OL,16,Fcourt.
OL,18,FMs Brown said: "The tears we have shed
OL,19,Fcould fill buckets, and I live with
OL,20,Fthe knowledge my son caused the death
OL,21,Fof my beloved father.
