OL,4,Ctwo people and killing grandfather
OL,6,F"Even though he's been in prison, we
OL,7,Fare still in fear. Mum is terrified he
OL,8,Fwill be back knocking at the door or
OL,9,Fher bedroom window.
OL,11,F"She lives in this fear constantly and
OL,12,Fwe fear the day he's released again."
OL,14,FMr Brown was well known in the local
OL,15,Fcommunity, having run a successful car
OL,16,Fpanel and body repair business thanks
OL,17,Fto his expertise in respect of vintage
OL,18,Fcars.
