OL,4,Ctwo people and killing grandfather
OL,6,FAt the opening of the case last week,
OL,7,Fprosecutor Michael Duck KC said that
OL,8,FWalpole had been "drinking throughout
OL,9,Fthe day" and committed two assaults at
OL,10,FBulkington Working Men's Club around
OL,11,Fan hour after attacking his
OL,12,Fgrandfather.
OL,14,FWalpole bought a small bottle of vodka
OL,15,Ffrom a shop in Bulkington at about
OL,16,F9am, before attending a match at
OL,17,FCoventry City's home stadium in the
OL,18,Fafternoon.
