OL,3,CMan jailed for 15 years for assaulting
OL,4,Ctwo people and killing grandfather
OL,6,FAfter attacking his grandfather,
OL,7,FWalpole smashed a pint glass over the
OL,8,Fback of a club member's head in an
OL,9,Fincident caught on the "clearest
OL,10,Fpossible" CCTV footage, before
OL,11,Fassaulting a bar worker while he was
OL,12,Fbeing physically removed from the club.
OL,14,FMr Brown's daughter installed security
OL,15,Fcameras at her parents' home in St
OL,16,FJames Gardens, Bulkington, because of
OL,17,FWalpole's "deteriorating" behaviour,
OL,18,Fand the pensioner was recorded in a
OL,19,F"haunting" video gesturing for help
OL,20,Ftowards the camera before the attack.
